episodes.title: The Hottest And Youngest In Hollywood Under 30
episodes.author: Jordan Harbinger
episodes.summary: Natalie Robehmed, staff writer at Forbes, shares the methods behind the choosing the glitz and celebrity 30 Under 30 Hollywood and Entertainment list. Robehmed dishes on your favorite TV, film and digital stars, the sad statistics behind diversity in the industry and what it takes to be a digital star.

episodes.title: People Under 30 Crushing It In Consumer Tech
episodes.author: Jordan Harbinger
episodes.summary: Brian Solomon is the Forbes staff writer in charge of curating the 30 Under 30 consumer tech list. In his chat with Jordan, we hear about a smart gun prototype, why Spectacles has a better shot than Google Glass and how the slow-moving, traditional real estate market could be upended.

episodes.title: Forbes Billionaires: The Wealthiest In The World
episodes.author: Jordan Harbinger
episodes.summary: Kerry Dolan, Assistant Managing Editor of Wealth at Forbes, curates the Forbes World Billionaires List. She shares how the wealthiest people on the planet made their money, how they spend it and the drastic measures one Billionaire took to get off the list.
